#### 3. **Compliance Features**
- **CSIR Guidelines Enforcement**:
  ```php
  // In application validation
  function validateEligibility($applicant, $vacancy) {
      // Check minimum qualification against CSIR guidelines
      $min_qual = getPostMinimumQualification($vacancy['post_id']);

      if ($applicant['degree'] !== $min_qual) {
          throw new Exception("Minimum qualification requirement not met (CSIR Guidelines Section 5.2)");
      }

      // Check age limit (35 years for Scientist)
      $dob = new DateTime($applicant['dob']);
      $age = $dob->diff(new DateTime())->y;
      if ($age > 35) {
          throw new Exception("Age limit exceeded (CSIR Recruitment Rules)");
      }
  }
  ```

- **GIGW Compliance**:
  - All forms encrypted at rest (AES-256)
  - Audit logs for all admin actions
  - GDPR-compliant data handling (data deletion API)
  - Secure file uploads (virus scanning via ClamAV)

#### 4. **Document Management**
```php
// File upload handler (applicant/upload.php)
if ($_FILES['document']['size'] > 0) {
    $allowed = ['pdf', 'docx', 'jpg', 'jpeg', 'png'];
    $ext = strtolower(pathinfo($_FILES['document']['name'], PATHINFO_EXTENSION));

    if (!in_array($ext, $allowed)) {
        die('Invalid file type');
    }

    $filename = uniqid('doc_') . '.' . $ext;
    $upload_path = 'uploads/documents/' . $filename;

    if (move_uploaded_file($_FILES['document']['tmp_name'], $upload_path)) {
        // Save to database
        $stmt = $pdo->prepare("INSERT INTO documents (application_id, document_type, file_path) VALUES (?, ?, ?)");
        $stmt->execute([$app_id, $_POST['doc_type'], $upload_path]);
    }
}
```

#### 5. **Telegram & SMTP Notifications**
```php
// includes/notifications.php
function sendNotification($applicant, $type, $vacancy) {
    // SMTP Notification
    $mail = new PHPMailer(true);
    $mail->isSMTP();
    $mail->Host = SMTP_HOST;
    $mail->Port = SMTP_PORT;
    $mail->SMTPAuth = true;
    $mail->Username = SMTP_USER;
    $mail->Password = SMTP_PASS;

    $mail->setFrom(SMTP_FROM, SMTP_NAME);
    $mail->addAddress($applicant['email']);
    $mail->Subject = "CSIR-SERC Application Status: " . $type;
    $mail->Body = "Your application for {$vacancy['title']} has been {$type}.";
    $mail->send();

    // Telegram Notification
    $bot_token = TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN;
    $chat_id = TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID;
    $message = "Application Status: {$applicant['name']} - {$type} for {$vacancy['title']}";

    file_get_contents("https://api.telegram.org/bot$bot_token/sendMessage?chat_id=$chat_id&text=" . urlencode($message));
}
```

#### 6. **Admin Backup System**
```php
// admin/backup.php
if (isset($_POST['generate_backup'])) {
    $backup_dir = 'backups/' . date('Ymd_His') . '/';
    mkdir($backup_dir, 0755, true);

    // Database dump
    exec("mysqldump -u " . DB_USER . " -p" . DB_PASS . " " . DB_NAME . " > " . $backup_dir . "db.sql");

    // Document backup
    copy('uploads/', $backup_dir . 'documents/', true);

    // Create ZIP
    $zip = new ZipArchive();
    $zip_file = 'backups/application_backup_' . date('YmdHis') . '.zip';

    if ($zip->open($zip_file, ZipArchive::CREATE) === TRUE) {
        $zip->addFile($backup_dir . 'db.sql', 'db.sql');
        $zip->addDir($backup_dir . 'documents', 'documents');
        $zip->close();
    }

    header('Content-Type: application/zip');
    header('Content-Disposition: attachment; filename=' . basename($zip_file));
    readfile($zip_file);
    exit;
}
```

